do_comment_on

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
do_comment_on -  This method allows the person to make a comment on a current rule.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int do_comment_on(int num)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^num%^RESET%^ - the id of the rule to comment on
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 on success, 0 on failure
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/room/council_chambers.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method allows the person to make a comment on a current rule.
Comments are only allowed by magistrates and only in the first two
phases.
.EP

